headline: Is Cboe Still Attractive After a 199% Five Year Surge and Premium Valuation?
summary: Wondering if Cboe Global Markets is still worth buying after such a strong run, or if the easy money has already been made? This breakdown will help you separate real value from simple momentum. The stock is sitting around $253.02 after gaining 28.8% year to date and 27.4% over the past year, with a 199.0% return over five years, even though the last month has seen a modest pullback of 3.0% and the last week has been roughly flat at 0.1%.
